Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.40,0:00:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌和最喜欢产生的距离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.30,0:00:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的惊险与推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.20,0:00:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谜样的中式旋转餐桌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.10,0:00:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兰的回忆因此复苏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.80,0:00:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.50,0:00:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.30,0:00:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就叫做 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.60,0:01:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿着小兰抽奖得到的餐券
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到横滨的中华街就餐的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里认识了电影工作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.70,0:01:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电影导演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.00,0:01:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,矶上海藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电影导演助理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊东基传
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.90,0:02:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.80,0:02:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北浦京吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.70,0:02:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制作人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.80,0:02:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端四朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.40,0:02:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并和他们一起就餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.90,0:02:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端竟然死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.60,0:02:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端的座位上没有检验出毒物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他使用过的盘子和湿毛巾上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却发现了毒物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.60,0:02:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐在死者旁边的毛利叔叔成了下毒的嫌疑人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哈哈哈哈 开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.90,0:02:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天是第一次来这家饭店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是初次见到川端先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么非杀他不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来就很可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.70,0:02:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你女儿第一次来这个饭店就被星探看中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.20,0:02:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有那么好的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.60,0:02:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.00,0:03:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们真的只是偶尔来到这个饭店…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.60,0:03:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.60,0:03:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸色不太好哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.70,0:03:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.70,0:03:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站得有点久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就过来坐一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想叔叔很快就会破案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.70,0:03:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.20,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 小兰气色十分不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.00,0:03:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不快点带她去医院的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.90,0:03:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中华街 雨中的似曾相识（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.60,0:03:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.90,0:03:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人调换有毒的湿毛巾是在换座位之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.20,0:04:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时坐在死者右边的你最可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.60,0:04:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 小兰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.10,0:04:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在厕所里发现了装毒物的容器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.10,0:04:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.90,0:04:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.10,0:04:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去厕所的时候把毛巾拿过去下毒的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说不是我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.10,0:04:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样犯人就绝对不是小五郎叔叔了哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.70,0:04:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为叔叔来了这个饭店就没去过厕所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且川端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是擦了弄洒的汤以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.90,0:04:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿着湿毛巾就换了座位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.30,0:04:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得谁都没法调换湿毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.40,0:04:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该还是有办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不让别人发现的换毛巾的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.30,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是利用了这个旋转餐桌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.90,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把下了毒的湿毛巾放在转盘的边上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果转得正好的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.00,0:05:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湿毛巾就正好掉在了川端的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么如何啊 你这个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.10,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然这个掉下来谁都会觉得奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.80,0:05:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是恰巧没被发现的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.70,0:05:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果用能够使毛巾掉下来的速度转桌子的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.80,0:05:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盘子啊碗啊的也都掉下来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.60,0:05:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.80,0:05:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手边就是自己的毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会用那个毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.60,0:05:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这倒也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.10,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.90,0:05:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得在我拿酱油和辣油的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好几次把桌子转过来马上又转了回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.70,0:06:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得那时桌上料理的排列顺序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.50,0:06:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按顺时针是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.50,0:06:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回锅肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.00,0:06:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青椒肉丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蟹黄炒蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.90,0:06:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糖醋里脊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后是蒸笼盖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酱油在糖醋里脊和皮蛋的中间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辣油在回锅肉和蒸笼盖子的中间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的座位顺序
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.10,0:06:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从被杀的川端顺时针下去依次是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.50,0:06:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.40,0:06:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.50,0:06:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北浦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.30,0:06:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.50,0:06:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,矶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.10,0:06:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后酱油总是在叔叔的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辣油总是在北浦的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端说过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.10,0:06:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际上我对蛋过敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一看到有蛋的菜就觉得恶心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一看到就觉得恶心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那边请注意一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.90,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.90,0:07:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 鉴定员叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.40,0:07:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有问题想问一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.20,0:07:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么啊 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.60,0:07:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们既然检验了菜里有没有毒的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旋转餐桌也检验了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.10,0:07:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些地方也检验了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.70,0:07:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里还没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么快点去检验吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小五郎叔叔是这么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.50,0:07:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个沉睡的小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.30,0:07:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个有毒的湿毛巾上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.30,0:07:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有沾上什么奇怪的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.30,0:07:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒物以外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.50,0:07:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淡茶色的污渍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.80,0:08:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闻起来那像是汤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.00,0:08:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 小弟弟你看到的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端把汤弄在了裤子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后用湿毛巾擦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.70,0:08:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那个时候沾上的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.20,0:08:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.40,0:08:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有沾上别的什么东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.70,0:08:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么特别的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.80,0:08:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有沾上别的什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.80,0:08:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我去告诉小五郎叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.30,0:08:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.90,0:08:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端不是被掉包了的湿毛巾毒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.00,0:08:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在他死了之后再调换的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那个人调换的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,证据应该还在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个桌子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.90,0:08:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人在厕所里在自己的湿毛巾上下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后在就餐中把自己的毛巾和死者的调包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.10,0:09:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在死者两边坐着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 小兰和柯南 没注意的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不明白啊 到底是怎么做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.40,0:09:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三位嫌疑人都是电影制作者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.10,0:09:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不是用看不见的绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把有毒的湿毛巾吊起来了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.80,0:09:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈…哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.90,0:09:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊嚏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的冷气太足了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.40,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.40,0:09:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,横沟警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.60,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.20,0:09:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听哥哥说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.30,0:09:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利小五郎一开始都说一些看起来很没用的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是假装的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.00,0:09:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一阵奇怪的声音和舞蹈后 态度完全改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.40,0:09:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像突然换了一个人一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.60,0:10:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.30,0:10:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过就是哥哥说得夸张了点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.70,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道那个奇妙的舞蹈就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.40,0:10:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猜疑就到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.30,0:10:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家能不能都坐回到座位上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.50,0:10:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案发时和被害人一起坐在桌子上的有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊东 矶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.50,0:10:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有北浦三人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.60,0:10:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 让我来仔细和你们说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃饭的时候到底发生了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.90,0:10:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡的小五郎的推理秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.00,0:10:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.80,0:10:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死者的座位上由横沟来代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.80,0:10:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从右边开始案发时顺次是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.90,0:10:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.90,0:10:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,矶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.80,0:11:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北浦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.70,0:11:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兰的座位上请别的警察代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.10,0:11:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.00,0:11:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.20,0:11:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿身体不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.30,0:11:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.30,0:11:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兰和死者中间位置上的柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.10,0:11:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.70,0:11:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.10,0:11:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始说明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.20,0:11:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,案发前发生的不可思议的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议的事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桌子的转盘啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.40,0:11:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人转那个转盘欺负我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.00,0:11:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.30,0:11:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.90,0:11:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小五郎叔叔面前的转盘上有酱油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.50,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把那个转到面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.50,0:12:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上又会转回到小五郎叔叔面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.70,0:12:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.70,0:12:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后想要拿北浦先生面前的辣油也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子转到附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.80,0:12:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又会马上转回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.70,0:12:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是谁在欺负我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.10,0:12:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.80,0:12:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.10,0:12:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个小鬼说的和案件有什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.30,0:12:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.10,0:12:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.60,0:12:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.30,0:12:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿凶手会自己露馅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.50,0:12:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小五郎叔叔这么说来着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己露馅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包子来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.00,0:12:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊 怎么在这种时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.80,0:12:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.20,0:12:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在审查中途的时候给这个孩子一个包子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.80,0:13:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利侦探是这么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.80,0:13:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.90,0:13:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.20,0:13:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,矶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好好想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.70,0:13:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是刚发生过杀人案的桌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.80,0:13:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道哪里沾了毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.60,0:13:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能让刚碰过桌子的孩子马上吃东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.00,0:13:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.20,0:13:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鉴定员刚检查过这个桌子 哪里都没有发现…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 正如矶上所说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还残留着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.10,0:13:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我们看不到的角落里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.00,0:13:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快给我说清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.00,0:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒下在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.80,0:13:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.60,0:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.80,0:13:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个旋转餐桌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.60,0:14:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手放在上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 如果像这个蟹黄炒蛋和皮蛋的盘子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.90,0:14:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠的很近 又都伸出来一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.50,0:14:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那…那样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能像这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用手指夹住桌子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.30,0:14:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.90,0:14:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.70,0:14:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个转盘的下面下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.00,0:14:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.50,0:14:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要让被害者碰这里也很难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这两道菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是被杀的川端讨厌的东西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.70,0:14:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.50,0:14:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是看到就觉得讨厌的食物呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端对蛋过敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.00,0:14:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请横沟警部确认一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害者所坐的 也就是你面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.20,0:15:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放着这两盘菜的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.70,0:15:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辣油在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.40,0:15:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北浦面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.00,0:15:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得小鬼在转动转盘的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人才会又把它转回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端为了避开那两个菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.70,0:15:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沾上了毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样好几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.10,0:15:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.80,0:15:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辣油是这样没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候酱油在小鬼面前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.10,0:15:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在取酱油的时候也会转回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了让他沾到毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.60,0:15:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里就一定要沾上毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下毒必须要在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.90,0:15:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接用手拿的北京烤鸭上来前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.40,0:15:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.30,0:15:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定会被谁碰到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说小鬼在取酱油的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.70,0:15:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人还没有下毒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.30,0:15:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.60,0:16:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是凶手看到了北京烤鸭上来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.40,0:16:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才要在两个盘子间的转盘上下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为柯南转动转盘 没有下成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就转回来好几次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.10,0:16:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酱油在你面前的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两盘菜面前的人就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.50,0:16:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说这个人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚在这里杀害了川端的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凶手哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.50,0:16:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,矶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.00,0:16:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.50,0:16:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么那个沾有大量毒物的湿毛巾是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个本来是矶上的毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.70,0:16:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在厕所下了毒以后回到座位上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.50,0:16:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那两个盘子之间的转盘上下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.60,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在川端倒下的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.20,0:17:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁乱把川端的湿毛巾调包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让人发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.60,0:17:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己的湿毛巾上也沾上了汤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是想把自己的湿毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变得和死者擦过裤子的湿毛巾一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只漏掉了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.50,0:17:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端的裤子是牛仔裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.10,0:17:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被你调包的川端的湿毛巾上沾有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和汤一起沾上的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.10,0:17:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔裤的蓝色污渍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.90,0:17:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.60,0:17:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个湿毛巾在矶上面前就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.20,0:17:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,矶上是凶手的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.00,0:17:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个毛巾还不能说是铁证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:17:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.20,0:18:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了嫁祸矶上而放在那里也是可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.60,0:18:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果是矶上的话会自己坦白的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.80,0:18:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才柯南摸了沾有毒的转盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.60,0:18:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要用手吃包子的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而被你制止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.80,0:18:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这说明你还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.00,0:18:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,良心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.30,0:18:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,良心吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.30,0:18:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端要是对理香也有点良心的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.80,0:18:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会做这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.30,0:18:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理香是一年前死的那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那是拍摄事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.60,0:19:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 那不是事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那完全是谋杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.50,0:19:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来演到最后那个镜头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.20,0:19:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替身演员应该和理香换了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.80,0:19:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川端是知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.10,0:19:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.10,0:19:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.20,0:19:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说理香和他说想自己演最后一幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果后果惨重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.30,0:19:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也只是笑过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.80,0:19:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喊停的机会要多少有多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.80,0:19:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.60,0:19:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说她是个新手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.80,0:19:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她当傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.00,0:19:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.60,0:19:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导演也是人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.00,0:19:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直看着摄像机镜头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就被她迷住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.10,0:20:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管她有多么大的缺点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.30,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不明白这一点的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.60,0:20:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一辈子也就这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.90,0:20:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.10,0:20:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回局里说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.90,0:20:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然你应该已经把毒药擦掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.30,0:20:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我对那个小孩坐视不管怎么办呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.90,0:20:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像川端那种没血没泪的人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.40,0:20:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会改变问询的措辞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.40,0:20:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会变得让你无话可说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.20,0:20:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.30,0:20:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.50,0:20:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是给了我良心的上帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.30,0:20:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会说谢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.00,0:21:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做的不错哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.50,0:21:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我作为导演觉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.00,0:21:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有你那个鬼一样的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.00,0:21:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我本来就是不信上帝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.10,0:21:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上真的有上帝吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.50,0:21:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个冷静的女人的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.20,0:21:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.80,0:21:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.20,0:21:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.50,0:21:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了天就该晴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.90,0:21:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.40,0:21:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像能听见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.30,0:21:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上真的有上帝吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.50,0:21:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.40,0:21:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错 天使从来没有对我微笑过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.20,0:21:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一次也没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.90,0:22:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.80,0:22:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.40,0:22:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那个时候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.30,0:22:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.00,0:22:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一也在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.10,0:22:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.30,0:22:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.70,0:23:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作起来 小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.90,0:23:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.50,0:23:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兰…小兰姐姐她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.70,0:23:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烧得那么厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.00,0:23:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.50,0:23:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.60,0:23:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.10,0:24:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.20,0:24:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.40,0:24:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点 兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.50,0:24:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.60,0:24:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.40,0:24:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是新一吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.70,0:24:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.10,0:24:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一NY事件（事件篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.90,0:24:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.30,0:24:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舞台服装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.60,0:24:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集的舞台是回忆中的纽约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.80,0:24:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点让人怀念的案件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.93,0:00:18.27,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.43,0:00:28.03,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,为了两人所说的未来中 能有个地方和你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.57,0:00:31.66,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.82,0:00:35.33,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,希望变成你的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.03,0:00:43.59,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,相信彼此牵着的手 誓言与你一起迈向前方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.66,0:00:50.39,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,“最讨厌”那种话 即使是谎言也说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.42,0:00:57.44,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,要说是“最喜欢” 如果是谎言我也不会说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.18,0:01:05.61,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就连无法见面的时候 也要让你无暇考虑别的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.33,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的心里只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.98,0:01:15.37,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop my love for you{\fn4YEOVAL}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.53,0:01:24.88,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,为了让两人的爱永不离去 拥抱对方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.75,0:01:32.06,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,不安的夜晚总会来临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.09,0:01:40.14,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,840)}那时候 请紧紧地将我抱在怀中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.87,0:22:27.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,每个清晨来临的时候都会想起你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.21,0:22:33.98,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只要待在你身旁就觉得好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.51,0:22:40.61,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕因时间的流逝而哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.85,0:22:45.84,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在渐渐改变的人的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.53,0:22:59.42,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有期望也就没有失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.25,0:23:06.22,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,然而不能没有追求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.50,0:23:13.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,无论前方是怎样的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.47,0:23:20.65,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,梦醒以后 你还是那么遥远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.93,0:23:26.20,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是自作多情的徒劳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.44,0:23:33.79,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,花雨中的道路还是没有丝毫改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.07,0:23:40.83,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,880)}真想挽着你的手漫步其中
